    {
      "id": "PopularPost240352",
      "post_content": "There are no bad cards, only cards with very weak interactions. that being said if i picked this 12-14 out of a pack in draft, I would be very pleased. 7 life four four mana at the end of an opponent's turn is nothing to scoff at, that is almost 40 percent of starting life total, that being said this will be one of the cards that gets passed around the table and no one wants to pick (barring an overzealous Timmy lured by the number 7) however this is a reasonable card in limited, no glitter or fire works but this is a good blue collar card",
