      "id": "PopularPost247403",
      "post_content": "This is inferior to [White Sun's Passage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=White Sun's Passage), which, at the time of this writing, is still in standard. Might be useful in limited or draft, though.  \n  \nPerhaps the designers were weary of printing powerful life gain cards because [Chalice of Life](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chalice of Life) is in the same block.",
      "posted_by": "MechaKraken",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost247403\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">This is inferior to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"White Sun's Passage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=White Sun's Passage\">White Sun's Passage</a>, which, at the time of this writing, is still in standard. Might be useful in limited or draft, though.<br/><br/>Perhaps the designers were weary of printing powerful life gain cards because <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chalice of Life\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chalice of Life\">Chalice of Life</a> is in the same block.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '247403'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy42650\">MechaKraken</span>\r\n                                (5/27/2012 11:29:53 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidS