    {
      "id": "PopularPost251819",
      "post_content": "Just to review:  \n  \nFor the same CMC [Congregate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Congregate) will give you more life (potentially a lot more), if there are 4 or more creatures on the battlefield.  \n  \nFor 2 mana [Heroes' Reunion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Heroes' Reunion) will give you the same amount of life, if you have green.  \n  \nFor 2 mana [Rest for the Weary](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rest for the Weary) will give you 1 more life, if you dropped a land that turn.  \n  \nFor 3 mana [Renewed Faith](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Renewed Faith) will give you just 1 less life, with the option of getting 2 life and a card draw for 2 mana instead.  \n  \nFor 2 mana [Whitesun's Passage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Whitesun's Passage) and [Soothing Balm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Soothing Balm) will give you just 2 less life.",
      "posted_by": "UncreativeNameMaker",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost251819\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Just to review:<br/><br/>For the same CMC <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Congregate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Congregate\">Congregate</a> will give you more life (potentially a lot more), if there are 4 or more creatures on the battlefield.<br/><br/>For 2 mana <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Heroes' Reunion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Heroes' Reunion\">Heroes' Reunion</a> will give you the same amount of life, if you have green.<br/><br/>For 2 mana <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rest for the Weary\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rest for the Weary\">Rest for the Weary</a> will give you 1 more life, if you dropped a land that turn.<br/><br/>For 3 mana <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Renewed Faith\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Renewed Faith\">Renewed Faith</a> will give you just 1 less life, with the option of getting 2 life and a card draw for 2 mana instead.<br/><br/>For 2 mana <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Whitesun's Passage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Whitesun's Passage\">Whitesun's Passage</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Soothing Balm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Soothing Balm\">Soothing Balm</a> will give you just 2 less life.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '251819'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy28296\">UncreativeNameMaker</span>\r\n                                (6/18/2012 2:39:52 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
